Package: odelia
Type: Package
Title: ODE Solver with Automatic Differentiation, in C++ Header Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Daniel", "Falster", , "daniel.falster@unsw.edu.au", c("aut", "cre"), 
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9814-092X")),
    person("Richard", "FitzJohn", , "", "aut"),
    person("Andrew", "O'Reilly-Nugent", , "", "aut")
    )
Maintainer: Daniel Falster <daniel.falster@unsw.edu.au>
Description: odelia provides an ODE solver in C++ header files, using an
    adaptive-step Runge-Kutta 4-5 method, with an interface to R via Rcpp.
    ODE systems can be templated on their scalar type to support automatic
    differentiation, enabling exact gradients for parameter fitting.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
